	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Author of a law regulating appointment of guardians in the provinces (Gaius 1.185, FIRA 2.44; Ulpian 11.18, FIRA 2.275). The date is uncertain, but may come after the Iulian law of 46, and may have been carried by the Tr. Pl. of 43. See Niccolini, FTP 443f." .
